OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1773087074
OL,3,CMo Farah and Gemma Collins among stars
OL,4,Cto return for I'm A Celeb South Africa
OL,6,FThe full line-up of I'm a A Celebrity
OL,7,FSouth Africa has been announced, with
OL,8,F12 former campmates, including the
OL,9,Flikes of Sir Mo Farah and Gemma
OL,10,FCollins, set to return to the
OL,11,Fcompetition.
OL,13,FJoining Sir Mo and Collina will be
OL,14,FScarlett Moffatt, Adam Thomas, Ashley
OL,15,FRoberts, David Haye, Beverley Callard,
OL,16,FSeann Walsh, Sinitta, Craig Charles,
OL,17,FJimmy Bullard and Harry Redknapp.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/5
