OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1773087074
OL,3,CMo Farah and Gemma Collins among stars
OL,4,Cto return for I'm A Celeb South Africa
OL,6,FIt is the second season of I'm a Celeb
OL,7,FSouth Africa, the spin-off show which
OL,8,Fswaps the Australian jungle for Kruger
OL,9,FNational Park and features returning
OL,10,Fcelebs as its main draw.
OL,12,FMoffatt was crowned Queen of the
OL,13,FJungle back in 2016, while Redknapp
OL,14,Fwon the show in 2018. Haye made it to
OL,15,Fthe final in 2012.
OL,17,FBullard had a less successful run in
OL,18,Fthe camp in 2014, and he was the first
OL,19,Fcampmate to be voted off.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/5
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
