PN,30403
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1773087074
OL,3,CMo Farah and Gemma Collins among stars
OL,4,Cto return for I'm A Celeb South Africa
OL,6,FThe campmates have all already proved
OL,7,Fthey can survive the gruelling
OL,8,Fbushtucker trials of the jungle, but
OL,9,Fin the South African Savannah, the
OL,10,Ftrials are even tougher.
OL,12,FThe pre-recorded series will begin on
OL,13,FMonday, April 6 and will air on ITV1,
OL,14,FSTV and ITVX. In a change to the
OL,15,Fformat, the winner will be decided by
OL,16,Fthe public during a live grand final
OL,17,Ffrom London on Friday, April 24.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/5
