OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1773087074
OL,3,CMo Farah and Gemma Collins among stars
OL,4,Cto return for I'm A Celeb South Africa
OL,6,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,7,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,8,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,9,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,11,FAnt McPartlin and Declan Donnelly will
OL,12,Freturn as hosts, with ITV saying the
OL,13,Fnew run will feature fresh trials and
OL,14,Fchallenges set against the South
OL,15,FAfrican landscape.
OL,17,FThe broadcaster has also said the
OL,18,Fsecond series will introduce a new
OL,19,Felement by giving viewers the final
OL,20,Fsay over who is crowned the 2026
OL,21,Fwinner.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/5
